<h1>Your Booking with TravelHome</h1>

<p>
  Hello <%= @traveler.username %>, this is a courtesy email from Travel Home. <br><br>

  You are currently booked for <%= @traveler.bookings.last.trip_name ? @traveler.bookings.last.trip_name : @traveler.bookings.last.listings.all.each {|t| title}%>. <br>

  The host has been notified of your booking for each listing you have reserved.<br>
  You should hear back within 5 business days and will be notified via email.<br>

  If you are logged in, you can find more details on your <%= link_to "traveler's page", traveler_url(@traveler) %>. <br>
  Otherwise, please<%= link_to "log in.", login_url %> <br><br>

  Thank you for using Travel Home.<br><br><br>

  Have a safe journey!

</p>
